                  <p><strong>Box Model and Aside, Code Academy, Navigation and Midterm.</strong>
                   This week we start to really increase the workload beginning with the box model 
                   and aside assignment. For the box model and aside assignment we focus on how to 
                   edit borders around the different structures and features of the page. The aside feature 
                   can be used to provide side notes or more information depending on its placement.
                   In navigation, we learn how to navigate to specific areas of our website and webpages 
                   using a redirect element both for internal and external navigation. Code Academy is an external
                   website we use to expand our learning and practice in web developement. There are many courses
